title: Lessons from 8 years of YouTube
description:
We started making videos together in 2012 and over the past 8 years we've learned a lot. This week we look back on our first videos ever and talk about the lessons we've learned over the past 8 years. Check out our latest YouTube Video here: https://youtu.be/hnxMlDLwD8Y
And if you are interested in trying out Skillshare you can sign up to get 2 months free here: https://skl.sh/colinandsamir4
